reviewText: great video to learn how to give your man a massage, combine it with earthly body edible massage oil (vanilla is favorite) and your man won't ever let you go ... smile

I did find this video pleasing from a beginner's standpoint.  It's not big on the educational technical aspect, but it does have some to help back what is being talked about and showed.  The video part of each taking a turn on how to listen and give to the other is great.  The most important aspect was that the one giving really listened to their partner and was totally present for them.  Emphasis was also placed on the one receiving staying in connection with the giver.  Hearing their true experience was very enlightening.

My wife and I purchased this video expecting something much different than what we got.  This video looks like it was filmed in 1985 with a $100 budget.  It is not helpful, interesting or instructive but borders on down right creepy.  If you are looking for a video to help improve your sex life, this video is not for you.
